metadata.name: Jolly Jalapenos #0001
metadata.description: A team of individuals came together and decided that they wanted to spice up the holiday season for the NFT community. Together they created a 10k hand-drawn avatar project. Programmatically generated to make each jalapeno unique. The Jolly Jalapenos will be donating to charities specifically aimed to help women and children around the world through Angel Protocol. We aim to highlight the importance of women in the NFT & Crypto space and give back our community.
